{
  "stem": "16214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I recall the first few visits of my other mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I was running after her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You know, when she was-- I remember, I recall one scene.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She came with-- I think it-- it was on a bus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was sort of an open truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And she came, and she walked on top of the truck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I started running after that truck, when she was leaving, and crying very much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But that was just, you know, really in the beginning, when I was with my real parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And my mother didn't know what to do with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I mean, she was extremely nice to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Understanding and she certainly allowed me to have all my pictures of the Jesus over my bed, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So I just continued having, you know, the pictures praying to the only God I knew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And as it turned out, both of my parents were not religious at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So it's not like I had something to learn from them, other than Roman Catholicism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "As a matter of fact my father hated religion with passion, my real father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And my mother is completely, totally not religious at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So I never was shown anything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So I stayed basically with Roman Catholicism for the rest of the time I was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And no matter how many times I would go to church and pray to God, whatever, I still was very discriminated against.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Kids were calling me a dirty Jew anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And it wasn't a pleasant atmosphere to live in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It's a very small town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Everybody knows everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And basically, you know, I recall some horrible things.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
